product.name: Mario + Rabbids Kingdom Battle - Nintendo Switch
product.shortDescription: Worlds collide in Mario + Rabbids Kingdom Battle! The Mushroom Kingdom has been torn apart by a mysterious vortex, transporting the chaotic Rabbids into this once-peaceful land. To restore order, Mario, Luigi, Princess Peach, and Yoshi must team up with a whole new crew made up of four Rabbids heroes! Together, they will battle with weapons through four worlds filled with combat, puzzles, and unpredictable enemies. Developed exclusively for the Nintendo Switch system, Mario + Rabbids Kingdom Battle is the best of the Mario and Rabbids franchises, combining all that you love about Marioâ€™s iconic universe with the side-splitting antics of the Rabbids.
product.detailedDescription:
Mario Rabbids Kingdom Battle - Nintendo Switch


Winner of over 50 E3 awards and nominations, including Best Strategy Game
 

  • Mario and Rabbids universes collide in this new adventure, exclusively on the Nintendo Switch system
     
  • Mario, Luigi, Princess Peach, and Yoshi join forces with four Rabbids heroes, each with their own unique personality
     
  • Choose to play solo or co-op in this turn-based combat adventure, or put your skills to the test in local versus mode
     
  • Battle with an arsenal of weapons through four new worlds filled with enemies, puzzles, and humorous fun

customerReviews.reviewText:
Five stars for the game, zero stars for the delivery! When delivered to our house this week,  it was delivered in a plastic bag so when my son opened the door he saw his Christmas gift. 
The other game we had was delivered in a regular manila envelope. I have no idea why it was like this. I've never ordered something and it shows up in a plastic bag.
GREAT GAME I only got it from BEST BUY very cool and good and GREAT I love it with all my heart if I could I want to put 1,000,000 STARS AND MORE I just love it buy it and see for your self
The shipping was surprisingly fast. I got it in 3 days. I like fast shipping so I can enjoy my game on the weekend and holiday. It's just in time. Love it.

Gifted this to my son for his 12th birthday. He loves it! The intro was funny with the rabbits dressed as Mario and Princess. 

Packaging it came in was in mint condition. 

I have to admit I was shopping around other retailers and Walmart was by far was the best price for this game.
At first play, thought this game was ok, after about 30 minutes of game play, I was hooked. Great game play, sufficiently complex but not overly complicated. Highly recommend.
The item and service is first class
I got a glitch deal on this game otherwise I wouldnt have gotten it. I really enjoy the game, its really fun.
Brought this product as a birthday gift

The game seems boring, though the beginning animation sequence is very entertaining- my kids asked if I can return it. It definitely is not like the other Mario games. The 2 player mode is a real let down! Apparently all that player 1 can do is control the camera and confirm movements, while the 2nd player controls a little bot. We will give it another try, maybe I can figure something out, but initially, not a good first impression ...
